  keywords  = {database management systems;natural language processing;program debugging;software engineering;StackOverflow;WordNet;WordSimSEDB;automated construction;automated software engineering;bug report categorization;code search;duplicate bug report detection;lexical database;natural language contents;natural language processing;software-specific word similarity database;Java;Measurement;Semantics;Software;Software engineering;Tuning;Vectors, rank1},
